âš ï¸ IMPORTANT about shared libraries

When you run the executable:

./output


You may get:

error while loading shared libraries: libstringutils.so


This is normal for beginners.

You must add:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=../src:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH


Or fix it inside CMake later (RPATH).

